text: Monika Estere Štube (born 15 September 1999) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club Talsu NSS and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers Category:Bradford City W.F.C. players Category:Latvian expatriate footballers Category:Latvian expatriate sportspeople in England Category:Expatriate women's footballers in England Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
